spans.text: All Hail to thee All-powerful Harmony
thy undisputed Sway , Her wondrous Works resigning to thy Care

the living Source of unborn Light
give birth To this fair form of Heaven and Earth

to move Around the radiant Sphere of Central Fire , A never ceasing , never silent Choir

the vocal Shell he strung , To which the Muses sung : Then first the Muses sung ; melodious Strains Apollo plaid , And Music first begun by thy auspicious Aid
